-- JPMorgan Names Miller International President; Cavanagh Will Head TSS Unit
-- Bill Koenig
-- 2010-06-22T12:33:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/jpmorgan-names-miller-international-president-cavanagh-will-head-tss-unit.html

          
          
             JPMorgan Chase & Co. said Heidi
Miller, head of Treasury & Securities Services, has been named
president of international.  
 The company also said Michael Cavanagh, chief financial
officer, will succeed Miller as CEO of TSS. Doug Braunstein,
head of investment banking, Americas, will succeed Cavanagh.  
          
          


  


        